body: Can we seriously just stop shitting on people for liking celebrities/youtubers??? Like, yeah, the absolute worship of these people is unhealthy & strange, but enjoying them as people really isn’t. You’re not better than anyone else bc you don’t “fangirl” over Markiplier or Gal Gadot or whoever. Like, jesus, chill the fuck out ppl. Not every person who likes a celebrity is a “mindless drone w brain rot” or whatever tf you elitist asshole are sayin these days. People are allowed to like people. It’s not that deep, Jan. Stop being such a pessimistic asshole & go outside.
